497
00:32:41,877 --> 00:32:44,295
<i>O terceiro escapou pelas portas de vidro.</i>

498
00:32:44,379 --> 00:32:47,048
<i>Isso culminou numa tentativa de fuga</i>

499
00:32:47,132 --> 00:32:51,427
<i>que a imprensa batizou
