636
00:41:58,558 --> 00:41:59,559
Sabe a cerca?

637
00:42:00,143 --> 00:42:02,312
Será que a retroescavadeira funciona?

638
00:42:02,395 --> 00:42:05,356
Vamos lá. Temos de tentar, né?

639
00:42:05,440 --> 00:42:06,816
Vamos agir em equipe

640
00:42:06,899 --> 00:42:09,527
